Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.98,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}豪華な品も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:03.78,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}派手な飾りも、
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.49,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}いらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.53,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}食卓囲もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.32,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}昨日のミスも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:11.16,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}不安な明日も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:12.33,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}添えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:14.83,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ、いらない何も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.71,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}凝った味付けも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:18.58,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}シャレた盛り付けも、
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:20.29,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}いらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.30,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}涙の味はも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:24.09,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}しょっぱいとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:26.09,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}最後にいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:29.47,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}笑えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:32.76,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}それがスパイス
